EN(STI)(diag)-67
Diagnostics for Engine Starting Failure
ENGINE (DIAGNOSTICS)
16.Diagnostics for Engine Starting Failure
A: PROCEDURE
1. Check of the fuel amount
2. Inspection of starter motor circuit <Ref. to EN(STI)(diag)-68, STARTER MOTOR CIRCUIT, Diagnostics for Engine Starting Fail-
ure.>
3. Inspection of ECM power supply and ground line <Ref. to EN(STI)(diag)-77, CHECK POWER SUPPLY AND GROUND LINE
OF ENGINE CONTROL MODULE (ECM), Diagnostics for Engine Starting Failure.>
4. Inspection of ignition control system <Ref. to EN(STI)(diag)-79, IGNITION CONTROL SYSTEM, Diagnostics for Engine Start-
ing Failure.>
5. Inspection of fuel pump circuit <Ref. to EN(STI)(diag)-81, FUEL PUMP CIRCUIT, Diagnostics for Engine Starting Failure.>
6. Inspection of fuel injector circuit <Ref. to EN(STI)(diag)-82, FUEL INJECTOR CIRCUIT, Diagnostics for Engine Starting Fail-
ure.>
